gOCCMake v1.0
-------------


gOCCMake is a standalone OCC-compiler for win32 (windows 9x, Me, NT, 2000 and
possibly XP).

The OCC technology is described at:

	http://www.schau.com/palm/occ/





Installation
------------


Extract the archive to c:\Program Files using WinZip or pkUnZip.   This will
create a directory, GOCCMAKE, containing three files:

GOCCMAKE.EXE	-	The compiler
LARGE.BMP	-	Default large icon
SMALL.BMP	-	Default small icon

Feel free to change the icons - see the link above for restrictions.





Kind regards,
Brian Schau
Author of OCC


